content: Yeah, I was worried about the transfer process, but I made sure to cycle the new tank before adding the fish. I also took my time to acclimate them properly, so fingers crossed everything will be okay. By the way, I've been experimenting with different types of food for my fish. I've been feeding them a mix of flakes, pellets, and frozen brine shrimp, and they seem to love it. Do you have any recommendations for other types of food I could try?
